title: Dad and Dave's Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. In the Yarraville train station you'll find this cafe and bake shop offers vegan food for brunch as well cakes and slices that are vegan and/or gluten-free like muffins and vegan banana bread. Possible to pre-order baked goods in bulk. Menu has fluffy vegan pancakes, vege stack, roast veggie foccacia, avocado smash on sourdough, soup of the day, weekly special, vegan curry pies, vegan ham toastie. Bonsoy is available for coffee. Homely atmosphere with free Wi-Fi.
